Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.16,0:00:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎 幽鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.64,0:00:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非要這麼做不可嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.12,0:00:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.25,0:00:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是肯定會痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.66,0:00:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我親自去告訴幽鬼丸也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.40,0:00:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一直認定的歸宿 溫柔的紅蓮姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.91,0:00:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻是自己的殺母仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.02,0:00:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.57,0:00:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想保密就按我的命令去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.27,0:01:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間不多了 抓緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.72,0:02:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.43,0:02:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在剛才的戰鬥中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙應該已經消耗了相當多的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.22,0:02:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成敗在此一舉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.11,0:02:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能給她喘息的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我來擴大搜索範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 那個晶遁忍者到底跑到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.82,0:03:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切忌著急
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果讓她逃掉 幽鬼丸就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受夠了 搞得這麼狼狽 糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個只剩半條人命了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.21,0:05:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼感覺意識越來越模糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然淪落到這般田地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在據點時 我們明明都能死裡逃生的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是捕捉三尾的封印啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來已經差不多要完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 幽鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說時間緊迫了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅蓮 快搞定他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅蓮姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.47,0:06:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算背叛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.18,0:06:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒打算和你過不去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.31,0:06:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過那個術的副作用太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.45,0:06:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請再給我一次機會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都這個時候了還說這些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是這樣維護幽鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手下幾乎盡失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己也已遍體鱗傷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種狀態下 還要繼續戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.94,0:06:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在能做的就是盡力…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.93,0:06:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 也有不使用幽鬼丸的辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.15,0:06:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過必須爭分奪秒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前提是你必須完全服從我的指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.41,0:06:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若有其他奇怪舉動而導致計劃失敗的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會毫不客氣地使用他的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:06:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:07:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 幽鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.22,0:07:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 只是帶他去安全的地方而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼作戰方案是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會將指示傳達給麟兒的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.79,0:07:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只管聽從便行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡 即便是三尾的力量也無法波及了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅蓮姐 不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.43,0:07:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經發過誓了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼了命也要去完成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在這裡不要亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.38,0:07:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說說作戰方案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快開始吧 時間寶貴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 根據兜提供的情報顯示
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護衛封印的有兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.36,0:08:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個使用暗器 一個擅長體術
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前已經突襲了他們一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計警戒會大大加強吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 由我去佯攻引開他們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當於誘餌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.22,0:08:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 就這麼辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.64,0:08:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個就交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.71,0:08:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的沒問題嗎 紅蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是充當誘餌的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩餘的查克拉已經足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只需集中注意力 尋找破壞封印的時機即可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三尾已經完全進入封印範圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 就這樣逐步縮小結界四方封陣的範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.92,0:08:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將三尾完全束縛住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.71,0:09:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.53,0:09:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來者何人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然只派兩個小鬼保護這麼重要的封印式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個術 難道你就是傳說中的晶遁忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.86,0:09:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵禦晶遁班不是去迎戰了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.59,0:09:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何是好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夾著尾巴逃跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.57,0:09:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.66,0:09:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想和傳說中的晶遁忍者交手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是年輕氣盛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉的小鬼們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 集中精力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包圍網已經縮得夠小了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 由四個方向開始進行封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.07,0:09:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將三尾完全封印
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結界四方封陣.封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來做你的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觸感有些不對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.18,0:10:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.73,0:10:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可惜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用結晶護住了身體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.66,0:10:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 這種對手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換平常早就解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:10:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從僅剩的查克拉來看 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最多還能使出一到兩個術
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這招來決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制失誤…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.90,0:11:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.44,0:11:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包圍網還未破裂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調整呼吸 重新嘗試將封印固定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.01,0:11:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.14,0:11:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復合忍術 蛤蟆鐵炮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 成功使出來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度的術順利使出是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到你了 晶遁忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何 只要把那個封印給…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如前輩預測一般
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.33,0:13:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已與敵人的佯攻部隊接觸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.95,0:13:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 敵人的戰鬥力並不構成任何威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,0:13:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後 小隊兵分兩路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小李和天天已前往保護封印組了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那邊情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.40,0:13:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比較複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管找到了破解晶遁的方法 可那傢伙卻跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也趕快前往支援封印班吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 結界就無法維持了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.41,0:14:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.91,0:14:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此驚人的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是三尾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結界被打破了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標出現了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.76,0:15:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 好恐怖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量如此巨大的衝擊波
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.79,0:15:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又在這麼危險的地方召喚我們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在可不是說這種話的時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的已經達成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.18,0:15:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來 你們就無法封印三尾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.74,0:15:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋 不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麟兒 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.98,0:15:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅蓮姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅蓮姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.53,0:18:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 給我住手 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兜那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎相當急於將幽鬼丸的能力給喚醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.73,0:18:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是強制引出的力量並非真正的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.52,0:18:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有心中燃起某種強烈慾望之時
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能使出連自己也難以置信的真正力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.04,0:19:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經見過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟當時一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.55,0:19:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.64,0:21:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅蓮 感動的再會已經結束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.71,0:21:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麟兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.96,0:21:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止了木葉的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.87,0:21:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也該帶上幽鬼丸撤了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.39,0:21:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.18,0:21:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過即便是為了大蛇丸大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:21:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也該搞好關係不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.14,0:21:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.89,0:22:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你是能控制怪物的幽鬼丸的催化劑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.60,0:22:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 紅色的山茶花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.51,0:22:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 今天的小劇場是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.73,0:22:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事不妙了 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.46,0:22:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事不好了 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.42,0:22:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於今天小劇場的問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.91,0:22:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個的話 這邊的劇本裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.19,0:22:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個啦 簡直難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.97,0:22:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劇本根本就是空白的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.81,0:22:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作人員偷懶去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.81,0:22:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是放棄現場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊達 給我滾出來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個留言 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.35,0:22:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用即興表演臨時頂著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.62,0:22:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光演本篇就已經夠累的了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.07,0:22:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.00,0:22:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我上演一場個人秀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.88,0:22:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這完美的身材…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.42,0:22:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣根本就無法吸引收視率嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.55,0:22:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是用我的美色來吸引男生們…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.59,0:22:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個 還不如來欣賞我的武器藏品…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.75,0:22:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 還是由作為主角的我來表演一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.73,0:22:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 怎麼覺得有些不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.16,0:22:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 終於趕上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.24,0:22:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.16,0:22:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 停住了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.79,0:22:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連顏色都…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.15,0:23:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊達 給我適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.58,0:23:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 就讓我來畫吧 監督
